    <h1>Skyscraper Technique</h1>
    <p class="description">A link building strategy that finds already-linked-to content, creates a demonstrably better version, then pitches the original's backlink sources. When executed with genuine content quality, it remains one of the <strong>most systematic editorial link building methods</strong> available.</p>
